# Genelis FAQ data and FAQPage schema generator


def section(heading, intro, cta_heading, cta_text, cta_button, cta_link_key, items):
    return {
        "heading": heading,
        "intro": intro,
        "cta_heading": cta_heading,
        "cta_text": cta_text,
        "cta_button": cta_button,
        "cta_link_key": cta_link_key,
        "items": [{"question": q, "answer": a} for q, a in items],
    }


FAQ_DATA = {}

FAQ_DATA["home"] = section(
    "Frequently Asked Questions",
    "Whether you're exploring Genelis for the first time or comparing different study platforms, here are answers to some of the most common questions about how Genelis works, who it is designed for, and how it helps students build stronger learning habits through one connected AI-powered learning experience.",
    "Still have questions?",
    "Experience how the Genelis Learning System brings together learning, practice, testing, analysis, and revision into one connected AI-powered learning experience.",
    "Start Learning",
    "start_learning",
    [
        ("What is Genelis?", "Genelis is an AI-powered learning platform designed for CBSE students in Classes 9 to 12. It brings together AI-generated notes, chapter-wise practice, mock tests, personalised performance insights, revision tools, and guided learning within a single connected workspace. At the heart of the platform is the Genelis Learning System, a structured approach that helps students learn, practise, test, analyse, improve, and reinforce their understanding instead of studying in disconnected steps. The goal is not just to help students prepare for exams, but to help them build stronger concepts and develop consistent learning habits throughout the academic year."),
        ("Who is Genelis designed for?", "Genelis is built primarily for CBSE students in Classes 9, 10, 11, and 12. Whether a student is preparing for school examinations, board exams, or looking for a more organised way to study, the platform adapts to different stages of preparation. Parents and educators can also use Genelis to support students by providing structured learning resources, personalised recommendations, and meaningful insights into academic progress."),
        ("Which classes does Genelis support?", "Genelis currently supports CBSE Classes 9, 10, 11, and 12 across major academic subjects aligned with the latest NCERT curriculum. Students can study chapter-wise, generate AI-powered notes, practise topic-specific questions, attempt mock tests, monitor their performance, and revisit difficult concepts using features such as the Wrong Question Notebook and Weak Area Detection, helping them focus revision where it matters most."),
        ("Is Genelis aligned with the latest CBSE and NCERT curriculum?", "Yes. Genelis is designed around the latest available CBSE curriculum and NCERT textbooks. Learning resources, AI-generated notes, practice material, and mock tests are regularly reviewed and updated to reflect curriculum changes. As official syllabus revisions are announced, the platform aims to incorporate those updates so students continue learning with content that remains relevant and aligned with current academic requirements."),
        ("How does AI improve the learning experience?", "Rather than replacing traditional learning, Artificial Intelligence helps personalise it. Within Genelis, AI assists students by generating structured notes, simplifying complex concepts, identifying weaker topics, recommending revision priorities, and providing performance insights based on learning behaviour. Combined with the Genelis Learning System and the AI Study Coach, these features help students understand what to study next instead of simply giving them more content."),
        ("Is Genelis free to use?", "Yes. Genelis offers a Free Plan that allows students to explore the platform and experience its core learning features before upgrading. Students who need higher usage limits, unlimited AI tools, advanced analytics, unlimited mock tests, and additional Premium features can choose a subscription plan that best matches their learning needs."),
        ("Can I use Genelis on both mobile and desktop?", "Yes. Genelis is accessible through modern web browsers on desktops, laptops, tablets, and most smartphones. This flexibility allows students to continue learning, revising, or practising from almost anywhere while maintaining the same connected learning experience across devices."),
        ("What makes Genelis different from tuition and other learning apps?", "Many students use separate resources for notes, practice questions, mock tests, revision, analytics, and performance tracking. Genelis brings these learning activities together into one connected platform. Through the Genelis Learning System, students can move naturally from learning concepts to practising questions, testing understanding, analysing performance, improving weaker areas, and reinforcing learning. Features such as the Wrong Question Notebook, Weak Area Detection, AI Study Coach, and Reattempt Mocks are designed to help students study more purposefully instead of simply spending more time studying."),
        ("Does Genelis provide AI-generated notes and summaries?", "Yes. Genelis generates structured AI-powered notes and chapter summaries to help students revise important concepts more efficiently. These notes are designed to complement classroom learning and NCERT textbooks by presenting key ideas in a concise, organised, and easy-to-review format. Students can also use the platform to revisit topics repeatedly as they progress through the Genelis Learning System."),
        ("Can Genelis help students prepare for board examinations?", "Genelis is designed to support long-term CBSE board exam preparation through structured revision, chapter-wise practice, mock tests, AI-powered performance analysis, and personalised learning recommendations. Features such as Weak Area Detection, Wrong Question Notebook, and Reattempt Mocks help students focus on concepts that require additional attention. While academic success ultimately depends on a student's effort, consistency, and understanding, Genelis aims to provide the tools, guidance, and insights needed to help students prepare with greater confidence and clarity."),
    ],
)

FAQ_DATA["learning_system"] = section(
    "Questions About the Genelis Learning System",
    "The Genelis Learning System is designed to make studying more structured, personalised, and effective. Instead of treating learning as separate tasks, it brings notes, practice, mock tests, performance analysis, revision, and AI guidance together into one connected experience.",
    "Ready to experience the Genelis Learning System?",
    "See how AI-powered notes, structured practice, mock tests, performance insights, and personalised guidance come together to help you learn more effectively.",
    "Start Learning",
    "learning_system_final",
    [
        ("What is the Genelis Learning System?", "The Genelis Learning System is a structured learning framework that guides students through every stage of preparation—from understanding concepts and practising questions to analysing performance, strengthening weak areas, and revising effectively. Rather than relying on multiple disconnected resources, it combines AI-powered notes, chapter-wise practice, mock tests, performance insights, and personalised guidance into one connected learning experience. The objective is to help students study with greater clarity, consistency, and confidence."),
        ("How does the Genelis Learning System work?", "The learning journey follows a structured sequence: Learn, Practice, Test, Analyse, Improve, and Reinforce. Students begin by building conceptual understanding through AI-generated notes and explanations, apply what they have learned through practice questions, evaluate their understanding with mock tests, review their performance using analytics, strengthen weaker areas through personalised recommendations, and reinforce concepts through continuous revision. This cycle helps transform learning into an ongoing process rather than a one-time activity."),
        ("How are AI notes generated?", "Genelis AI creates structured notes based on the selected chapter or topic while keeping the content aligned with the latest available CBSE and NCERT curriculum. The notes focus on explaining important concepts, highlighting key points, and presenting information in a clear and organised format. They are designed to support classroom learning and revision, helping students review topics more efficiently without replacing their textbooks or teacher's guidance."),
        ("Does Genelis create personalised study plans?", "Yes. As students interact with the platform, Genelis AI analyses learning patterns, performance, and progress to provide personalised recommendations. Instead of suggesting the same revision schedule for every learner, the platform prioritises topics that may require additional attention, helping students use their study time more effectively while maintaining balanced preparation across subjects."),
        ("How does Genelis identify weak areas?", "Genelis continuously analyses practice sessions, mock test performance, and learning behaviour to identify concepts that require further attention. Rather than focusing only on overall marks, the platform looks for recurring mistakes and patterns across chapters. These insights help students understand where they need additional revision and allow them to focus on improving concepts before moving forward."),
        ("How are mock tests generated?", "Genelis offers chapter-wise and subject-wise mock tests designed around the latest CBSE exam patterns. Questions are selected to encourage conceptual understanding and application rather than simple memorisation. After each attempt, students receive performance insights that highlight strengths, identify weaker topics, and support more focused revision for future attempts."),
        ("What is the Wrong Question Notebook?", "The Wrong Question Notebook is a revision tool that automatically collects questions answered incorrectly during practice sessions and mock tests. Instead of repeating the entire syllabus, students can revisit their previous mistakes in one place, understand why the correct answer is right, and strengthen concepts that need additional practice. This encourages continuous improvement through targeted revision."),
        ("Can I reattempt mock tests after improving?", "Yes. Genelis allows students to reattempt eligible mock tests after completing additional study and revision. Reattempting helps students measure improvement over time, reinforce concepts, and build confidence by comparing their performance across multiple attempts rather than relying on a single score."),
        ("How does the AI Study Coach support learning?", "The AI Study Coach provides guidance throughout the learning journey by helping students decide what to study next, suggesting revision priorities, encouraging consistent learning habits, and supporting preparation based on individual progress. Instead of replacing independent thinking, it acts as a learning companion that helps students make more informed study decisions."),
        ("How does the Genelis Learning System help improve exam preparation?", "Effective exam preparation requires more than completing the syllabus. The Genelis Learning System combines conceptual learning, structured practice, mock testing, performance analysis, personalised recommendations, and continuous revision into one connected process. By helping students identify weaker areas, revisit previous mistakes, and study more strategically, the platform supports consistent progress while encouraging deeper understanding and long-term retention."),
    ],
)

FAQ_DATA["pricing"] = section(
    "Subscription & Pricing Questions",
    "Choosing the right learning plan is an important decision. Below are answers to some of the most common questions about Genelis subscriptions, Premium features, payments, billing, and account management to help you make an informed choice.",
    "Still deciding which plan is right for you?",
    "Start with the Free Plan and experience how the Genelis Learning System supports smarter learning through AI-powered notes, structured practice, mock tests, and personalised learning insights. When you're ready, upgrading to Premium is just a few clicks away.",
    "Start Learning",
    "pricing_free",
    [
        ("What is included in the Free Plan?", "The Free Plan allows students to explore the core Genelis experience before deciding whether to upgrade. It includes access to selected AI-powered learning features, limited AI notes, AI doubts, chapter-wise practice, mock tests, personalised learning insights, and the Genelis Learning System. The Free Plan is designed to help students understand how the platform works while providing meaningful support for everyday learning."),
        ("What additional features are included in the Premium Plan?", "The Premium Plan unlocks the complete Genelis experience with higher usage limits and unrestricted access to learning tools. Depending on the selected plan, students can enjoy unlimited AI Notes, unlimited AI Doubts, unlimited chapter-wise and subject-wise mock tests, Wrong Question Notebook, Reattempt Mocks, PDF downloads, advanced learning features, and future Premium enhancements as they become available. Premium is designed for students who want uninterrupted access throughout their academic preparation."),
        ("Can I upgrade my subscription at any time?", "Yes. Students can upgrade from the Free Plan to a Premium Plan whenever they choose. Once payment is successfully completed, Premium features are activated automatically for the subscribed account, allowing students to continue learning without interruption."),
        ("Can I switch from a Monthly Plan to an Annual Plan?", "Yes. Students who begin with a Monthly Plan can upgrade to the Annual Plan whenever they wish. The Annual Plan is designed for students preparing over a longer period and provides uninterrupted access to Premium features throughout the subscription period."),
        ("Which payment methods does Genelis support?", "Genelis supports secure online payments through trusted payment partners. Depending on availability, students may be able to pay using UPI, debit cards, credit cards, net banking, and other supported digital payment methods. Available payment options are displayed during the checkout process."),
        ("Are subscriptions renewed automatically?", "Subscription renewal depends on the payment settings and plan selected during purchase. Where automatic renewal is available, students will continue receiving Premium access unless the subscription is cancelled before the renewal date. Any applicable renewal information will be clearly presented during the subscription process."),
        ("Is my payment information secure?", "Yes. Genelis does not store sensitive payment information such as complete card details or banking credentials. Payments are processed through trusted payment gateways that use industry-standard security measures to help protect financial transactions. Students should always ensure they are completing payments through the official Genelis website."),
        ("What happens if my payment is successful but Premium isn't activated immediately?", "In most cases, Premium access is activated automatically within a few moments after a successful payment. If there is a temporary delay due to payment processing or network issues, please allow a short period for the transaction to complete before refreshing your account. If your payment has been successfully debited but Premium access is still unavailable after a reasonable amount of time, please contact the Genelis Support Team at support@genelis.in with your registered email address, Payment ID, Order ID, and any relevant transaction details. To ensure the safety of your account, Premium subscriptions are activated only after successful payment verification."),
        ("Can I request a refund?", "Refund eligibility depends on the circumstances and is governed by the Genelis Refund & Cancellation Policy. Students who experience payment-related issues or believe they qualify for a refund can contact the Genelis support team with the relevant transaction details. Each request is reviewed in accordance with the applicable policy."),
        ("Will I automatically receive new Premium features?", "Yes. As Genelis continues to introduce new Premium features and improvements, eligible subscribers will generally receive access to those features as part of their active subscription unless otherwise stated. This allows students to benefit from ongoing platform enhancements without requiring a separate purchase for every new feature."),
        ("Why should I choose Premium over the Free Plan?", "The Free Plan is ideal for exploring Genelis and experiencing its core learning capabilities. Premium is intended for students who want uninterrupted access to the complete learning experience throughout the academic year. With unlimited AI-powered tools, comprehensive mock tests, structured revision support, advanced learning features, and personalised insights, Premium enables students to study more consistently while making full use of the Genelis Learning System."),
    ],
)

FAQ_DATA["about"] = section(
    "About Genelis",
    "Genelis was created with a simple belief: learning should be more personalised, structured, and accessible for every student. Below are answers to some of the most common questions about our mission, values, approach to AI, and the vision behind the platform.",
    "Have more questions about Genelis?",
    "The best way to understand how Genelis supports learning is to experience it yourself. Explore the platform, discover the Genelis Learning System, and see how AI can help make learning more structured, personalised, and effective.",
    "Start Learning",
    "about_primary",
    [
        ("Why was Genelis created?", "Genelis was created to simplify the way students learn. Many learners rely on multiple resources for notes, practice questions, mock tests, revision, and performance tracking, making preparation fragmented and time-consuming. Genelis brings these essential learning activities together into one connected platform, helping students stay organised while making better use of their study time. Our goal is to support meaningful learning rather than simply increasing the amount of content students consume."),
        ("What is the mission of Genelis?", "Our mission is to make quality learning more personalised, accessible, and effective through responsible use of Artificial Intelligence. We aim to help students develop stronger conceptual understanding, better study habits, and greater confidence by providing tools that support every stage of their learning journey rather than focusing only on examination outcomes."),
        ("Is Genelis an educational institution?", "No. Genelis is a technology platform that supports learning through AI-powered educational tools and study resources. It is not a school, college, coaching institute, examination authority, or certification body. Students should continue to learn from their teachers, schools, textbooks, and official educational resources while using Genelis as a complementary learning companion."),
        ("How does Genelis use Artificial Intelligence responsibly?", "Artificial Intelligence is designed to support—not replace—learning. Genelis AI helps students generate notes, understand concepts, identify weak areas, receive personalised recommendations, and organise revision more effectively. While every effort is made to provide accurate educational assistance, students are encouraged to verify important information using their textbooks, teachers, and official CBSE or NCERT resources whenever appropriate."),
        ("Does Genelis replace teachers or coaching?", "No. Genelis is designed to complement classroom learning rather than replace teachers or coaching. Teachers provide guidance, experience, and personal interaction that technology cannot replicate. Genelis supports this process by helping students revise independently, practise regularly, monitor their progress, and make better-informed decisions about what to study next."),
        ("What makes Genelis different from other learning platforms?", "Genelis combines multiple stages of learning into one connected experience through the Genelis Learning System. Instead of switching between separate tools for notes, revision, mock tests, analytics, and performance tracking, students can manage their learning journey within a single platform. AI-powered insights help students focus on understanding concepts, identifying weaker areas, and building consistent study habits over time."),
        ("How do you ensure the quality of educational content?", "Educational content is developed with the objective of supporting the latest available CBSE and NCERT curriculum. AI-generated content is continually refined, while the platform is regularly improved based on user feedback, curriculum updates, and ongoing evaluation. Since AI-generated responses may occasionally contain inaccuracies, students should use Genelis alongside official educational resources and classroom instruction."),
        ("How can I share feedback or suggestions?", "We believe continuous improvement begins with listening to our users. Students, parents, educators, and other users are encouraged to share feedback, suggestions, feature requests, or report issues through the in-platform Feedback section or by contacting the Genelis Support Team. User feedback plays an important role in helping us improve both the platform and the overall learning experience."),
        ("Is Genelis continuously improving?", "Yes. Education and technology continue to evolve, and so does Genelis. We regularly introduce improvements, refine AI capabilities, enhance learning features, strengthen platform performance, and respond to curriculum changes where appropriate. Our objective is to build a platform that continues to grow alongside the needs of students and educators."),
        ("What is the long-term vision for Genelis?", "Our long-term vision is to build an intelligent learning platform that helps students learn with greater confidence, independence, and understanding throughout their academic journey. We aim to combine responsible Artificial Intelligence with thoughtful educational design to make learning more personalised, engaging, and accessible while continually improving the experience based on real student needs."),
    ],
)

FAQ_DATA["contact"] = section(
    "Need Help? Start Here",
    "Whether you have a question about Genelis, need assistance with your account, want to report a technical issue, or simply wish to share feedback, we're here to help. Below are answers to some of the most common support-related questions.",
    "Still need assistance?",
    "We're committed to providing a helpful, respectful, and transparent support experience. If you couldn't find the answer you were looking for, please get in touch and we'll do our best to assist you.",
    "Email Support",
    "Contact Support",
    [
        ("How can I contact Genelis?", "You can contact the Genelis Support Team by emailing support@genelis.in. Whether you have questions about your account, subscriptions, technical issues, AI-generated content, or general enquiries, our team will make reasonable efforts to assist you as promptly as possible."),
        ("What are your support hours?", "Our support team reviews enquiries during regular business hours. While response times may vary depending on the nature and volume of requests, we aim to respond as quickly as reasonably possible. Some complex technical, billing, or legal matters may require additional investigation before a complete response can be provided."),
        ("How long does it take to receive a response?", "We strive to acknowledge enquiries within a reasonable timeframe and respond as quickly as possible. Simpler questions may be resolved sooner, while technical investigations, payment-related matters, or requests requiring additional verification may take longer. We appreciate your patience while we work to resolve each request thoroughly."),
        ("How do I report a technical issue?", "If you encounter a technical problem while using Genelis, please contact us at support@genelis.in with as much detail as possible. Including your registered email address, device information, browser, screenshots, error messages, and the steps that led to the issue helps us investigate and resolve the problem more efficiently."),
        ("How can I report incorrect AI-generated content?", "Although Genelis AI is designed to generate helpful educational content, AI-generated responses may occasionally contain inaccuracies or require clarification. If you identify content that appears incorrect, outdated, or misleading, please report it through the in-platform Feedback section or by emailing support@genelis.in. Your feedback helps us improve both the quality and reliability of the platform."),
        ("How do I report a payment or subscription issue?", "If you experience a payment failure, duplicate charge, delayed subscription activation, or any other billing-related concern, please contact the Genelis Support Team with your registered email address, Payment ID, Order ID, and any relevant transaction details. Providing complete information allows us to investigate the issue and assist you more efficiently."),
        ("Can I submit feature requests or suggestions?", "Yes. We welcome ideas from students, parents, and educators. If there is a feature you would like to see on Genelis or you have suggestions for improving the platform, you can submit them through the in-platform Feedback section or by contacting us directly. Many platform improvements are inspired by valuable feedback from our user community."),
        ("How can I report a security issue?", "If you believe you have discovered a security vulnerability or suspect unauthorised activity affecting Genelis, please contact us immediately at support@genelis.in and include Security Issue in the subject line of your email. Providing a detailed description of the issue will help us investigate and take appropriate action as quickly as possible."),
        ("Where can I submit feedback or raise a grievance?", "Genelis provides multiple ways to share feedback, report concerns, or raise formal grievances. Users may use the in-platform Feedback section to submit suggestions, feature requests, technical issues, or educational content concerns. For formal grievances, users may also contact the designated Grievance Officer through the contact details provided in our Grievance Redressal Policy."),
        ("Who should I contact regarding legal, copyright, or privacy concerns?", "For questions relating to copyright, intellectual property, privacy, data protection, or other legal matters, please contact the Genelis Support Team at support@genelis.in with complete details of your request. Where appropriate, your enquiry will be directed to the relevant team for review and response in accordance with our applicable policies."),
    ],
)

